 Port Elizabeth businessman Christopher Panayiotou has just been found guilty of the murder of his wife, Jayde.
Judgment was handed down in the Port Elizabeth High court today (02/11/17), on Panayiotou’s 31st birthday.
Sentencing will take place 17 November, 2017 at 9:30am.
